  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The DIETary intake, death and hospitalisation in adults with end-stage kidney disease treated
      with HaemoDialysis (DIET-HD) study is a multinational prospective cohort study designed to
      evaluate the association between nutrition and dietary patterns and health outcomes in
      prevalent adult haemodialysis patients in Europe and South America.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
